				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "##wiki-plugin-graphviz\nchange the way we freeze algorithmic diagrams with UX more like the map plugin\nmaybe move the static diagram code into a new wiki-dot-plugin\nrelated tools for page migration\ntest scafolding and automated tests"
